reviewText: Taylor Mason is unbelievably gifted, and it really shows in this video.  If we have a Ventriloquist Comedian Laureate, it should be he.  There is so much hilarious stuff here, and the way Taylor interacts with the audience is just wonderful. I just love the bit in the extras (which, BTW, there are a lot of) where we see the world through Romeo's eyes. Brilliant!

Very funny, and the proceeds go to feed starving children! ([...]) very long, a lot of extra stuff! This seems to be lie a best of for Taylor, but with a lot of new stuff. Taylor is one of the funniest, cleanest comedians Ai have ever seen!
